    eyebrowEn:'Original · Shaken · ABV ~18%', eyebrowZh:'原创 · 摇制 · 酒精度约18%',
    titleEn:'See You Tomorrow', titleZh:'明日再见',
    metaEn:[['Method','Shaken'],['Glass','Chilled coupe'],['Ice','Shake with ice, serve up'],['Garnish','Expressed orange peel']],
    metaZh:[['手法','摇制'],['酒杯','冰镇碟形杯'],['冰块','加冰摇制，滤冰上桌'],['装饰','橙皮卷']],
    ingrEn:['<strong>1.5 oz (45ml)</strong> Aged rum (Ron Zacapa or similar)','<strong>½ oz (15ml)</strong> Amaro Nonino','<strong>½ oz (15ml)</strong> Fresh lemon juice','<strong>¼ oz (7ml)</strong> Honey syrup (2:1 honey to water)','<strong>2 dashes</strong> Peychaud\'s bitters'],
    ingrZh:['<strong>1.5 oz (45ml)</strong> 陈年朗姆酒（推荐Ron Zacapa或同类）','<strong>½ oz (15ml)</strong> 诺尼诺阿马罗','<strong>½ oz (15ml)</strong> 新鲜柠檬汁','<strong>¼ oz (7ml)</strong> 蜂蜜糖浆（蜂蜜:水=2:1）','<strong>2滴</strong> 佩乔苦精'],
    stepsEn:['Combine all ingredients in a shaker with ice.','Shake for 12 seconds.','Double-strain into a chilled coupe.','Express an orange peel over the surface — hold it above the glass and snap it firmly to release the oils. Run it around the rim, then rest it on the edge.'],
    stepsZh:['将所有材料加入装有冰块的摇壶。','摇12秒。','双重过滤至冰镇碟形杯。','在杯面上方扭转橙皮取油——用力折压，让油脂喷洒在酒液表面。擦一圈杯口，搭在杯沿。'],
    notesEn:"This is the drink I make at the end of a long night behind the bar — for myself or for whoever is still there. The aged rum gives it warmth and depth, the Amaro Nonino adds a bittersweet complexity, and the honey softens everything without losing the edges. The name came naturally: it is the kind of drink that feels like a quiet goodbye. Not dramatic. Just — see you tomorrow.", notesZh:'这是我在吧台后漫长一夜结束时调的那杯酒——为自己，或者为还留在那里的人。陈年朗姆带来温度和深度，诺尼诺阿马罗增添苦甜的层次，蜂蜜将一切柔和而不失棱角。名字自然而然地来了：这杯酒有一种安静告别的感觉。不戏剧化。只是——明日再见。'
  },
