    notesEn:"Bryan Evans is the funniest British old man I have ever met behind a bar. He has the kind of beard that belongs in a folk song and the kind of laugh that fills a room before the joke is even finished.\n\nI earned my New York bartending certification under his instruction. The certificate is somewhere in a drawer. The things he taught me are not.",
